\\
dln\left(e_{t}^{h,f}\right) & = & \left((r_{t}^{N,h}-r_{t}^{N,f})-(r_{t}^{R,h}-r_{t}^{R,f})\right)dt
\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset

We can then compare the model's implied exchange rates to realized exchange
 rates.
